---
// Hero Section - Main landing page hero
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-purple-900 to-slate-900">
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] bg-center [mask-image:linear-gradient(180deg,white,rgba(255,255,255,0))]"></div>
  
  <!-- Language Selector -->
  <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10">
    <div class="flex gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-2">
      <button class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded text-sm font-medium">🇧🇷 PT</button>
      <button class="px-3 py-1 text-white/70 hover:text-white rounded text-sm">🇺🇸 EN</button>
      <button class="px-3 py-1 text-white/70 hover:text-white rounded text-sm">🇪🇸 ES</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-20 pb-16">
    <!-- Launch Badge -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400/20 to-orange-400/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-yellow-400/30 rounded-full px-6 py-3">
        <span class="text-yellow-400 text-lg">✨</span>
        <span class="text-yellow-100 font-medium">Lançamento — De R$ 2.997,00 por R$ 197,00</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column - Content -->
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Seu Estúdio de Vídeo IA
          </span>
          <br>
          <span class="text-white">Pessoal</span>
        </h1>
        
        <div class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-blue-300 font-semibold mb-4">
          Criação, Automação e Monetização
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-lg text-yellow-400 font-medium mb-8">
          100% no Seu Controle.
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-xl lg:max-w-none">
          Tecnologia avançada de IA que transforma suas ideias em vídeos profissionais para YouTube, TikTok e Instagram. Processamento local, sem dependência de serviços externos.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Buttons -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start mb-8">
          <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-purple-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200 shadow-2xl">
            Quero Começar Agora
          </button>
          <button class="border-2 border-white/30 hover:border-white/50 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-200">
            Ver Como Funciona
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust Indicators -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-blue-400 text-2xl mb-2">📹</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold">Acesso Vitalício</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Sem Mensalidades</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-green-400 text-2xl mb-2">🛡️</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold">Garantia Blindada</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">7 Dias</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-purple-400 text-2xl mb-2">🤖</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold">Tecnologia IA</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">100% Local</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-yellow-400 text-2xl mb-2">🎯</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold">Setup Simples</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">1 Hora</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Visual -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Main Video Preview -->
        <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-2xl">
          <div class="bg-black rounded-lg aspect-video flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-white text-6xl mb-4">📹</div>
              <div class="text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Demonstração do Sistema</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400">Veja como funciona na prática</div>
              <div class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl mt-4">12:47</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Play Button Overlay -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-full p-6 shadow-2xl transform hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-200">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating Stats -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-green-500 text-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold">2.847+</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Clientes Ativos</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-purple-500 text-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold">300+</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Vídeos/mês</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom Tagline -->
  <div class="text-center pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
      Sua Máquina, Suas Regras, Seus Lucros — Para Sempre
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      Enquanto seus concorrentes pagam fortunas mensais para ferramentas de nuvem e ficam limitados por cotas, você terá liberdade total para operar 24/7, gerando renda enquanto dorme, sem depender de ninguém.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
